# 📁 University Academic Management System — Project Structure

## Overview

```
University Academic Management System/
├── server/          ← Laravel Backend (PHP)         [ACTIVE - php artisan serve]
├── client/          ← React Frontend (Vite)          [ACTIVE - npm run dev]
├── backend/         ← Older/duplicate Laravel backend (not actively used)
├── frontend/        ← Older/duplicate React frontend (not actively used)
├── database/        ← (extra folder, likely legacy)
├── docs/            ← Documentation files
├── demo-checklists/ ← Testing checklists
└── *.md             ← Various project docs & status files
```

> **Note:** `server/` and `client/` are the **active** directories. `backend/` and `frontend/` appear to be older or duplicate copies.

---

## 🖥️ BACKEND — `server/` (Laravel 10+)

```
server/
├── .env                          ← Database config, app key, CORS settings
├── artisan                       ← Laravel CLI entry point
├── composer.json                 ← PHP dependencies
│
├── app/
│   ├── Http/
│   │   ├── Controllers/
│   │   │   ├── AuthController.php           ← Login, logout, token management
│   │   │   ├── Controller.php               ← Base controller
│   │   │   ├── CourseController.php         ← CRUD for courses
│   │   │   ├── CourseOfferingController.php ← Course offering management
│   │   │   ├── DepartmentController.php     ← CRUD for departments
│   │   │   ├── EnrollmentController.php     ← Student enrollment logic
│   │   │   ├── ResultController.php         ← Student results/grades
│   │   │   ├── SemesterController.php       ← Semester management
│   │   │   ├── StudentController.php        ← Student profile & data
│   │   │   ├── TeacherController.php        ← Teacher profile & data
│   │   │   └── UserController.php           ← General user operations
│   │   │
│   │   └── Middleware/                      ← Auth middleware (JWT/Sanctum)
│   │
│   ├── Models/
│   │   ├── User.php              ← Auth user (all roles: admin, teacher, student)
│   │   ├── Student.php           ← Student profile (linked to User)
│   │   ├── Teacher.php           ← Teacher profile (linked to User)
│   │   ├── Course.php            ← Course info
│   │   ├── CourseOffering.php    ← Course assigned to teacher+semester
│   │   ├── Department.php        ← Academic departments
│   │   ├── Enrollment.php        ← Student ↔ CourseOffering enrollment
│   │   ├── Result.php            ← Student grades/results
│   │   ├── Attendance.php        ← Attendance records
│   │   ├── MarksEntry.php        ← Marks entered by teacher
│   │   ├── Payment.php           ← Student payment records
│   │   ├── Semester.php          ← Semester info
│   │   └── AdminLog.php          ← Admin activity log
│   │
│   ├── Services/                 ← Business logic layer
│   └── Providers/                ← Laravel service providers
│
├── routes/
│   ├── api.php                   ← All API routes (used by frontend)
│   ├── web.php                   ← Web routes (minimal)
│   └── console.php               ← Artisan console routes
│
├── database/
│   ├── migrations/               ← Database table definitions
│   │   ├── create_users_table.php
│   │   ├── create_departments_table.php
│   │   ├── create_semesters_table.php
│   │   ├── create_teachers_table.php
│   │   ├── create_students_table.php
│   │   ├── create_courses_table.php
│   │   ├── create_course_offerings_table.php
│   │   ├── create_enrollments_table.php
│   │   └── create_results_table.php
│   │
│   └── seeders/                  ← Sample/test data
│       ├── DatabaseSeeder.php    ← Master seeder (calls all others)
│       ├── UserSeeder.php        ← Creates 6 admins, 55 teachers, 280 students
│       ├── StudentSeeder.php     ← Student profile records
│       ├── TeacherSeeder.php     ← Teacher profile records
│       ├── DepartmentSeeder.php  ← Academic departments
│       ├── SemesterSeeder.php    ← Semester records
│       ├── CourseSeeder.php      ← Course records
│       ├── CourseOfferingSeeder.php  ← Course ↔ Teacher assignments
│       ├── EnrollmentSeeder.php  ← Student course enrollments
│       └── ResultSeeder.php      ← Sample grades
│
├── config/                       ← Laravel config files (auth, cors, db, etc.)
├── bootstrap/
│   └── app.php                   ← App bootstrapping & middleware registration
├── public/
│   └── index.php                 ← Web server entry point
├── storage/                      ← Logs, cache, uploaded files
└── resources/                    ← Blade views (minimal, mostly API-only app)
```

