## 🌐 FRONTEND — `client/` (React + Vite)

```
client/
├── index.html                    ← HTML entry point
├── vite.config.js                ← Vite build config
├── package.json                  ← JS dependencies (React, React Router, Axios, etc.)
│
└── src/
    ├── main.jsx                  ← React app entry point
    ├── App.jsx                   ← Root component (wraps router + context)
    ├── App.css                   ← Global app styles
    ├── index.css                 ← Base/reset CSS
    │
    ├── api/
    │   └── apiService.js         ← Axios API calls to Laravel backend
    │
    ├── context/
    │   └── AuthContext.jsx       ← Global auth state (user, token, login/logout)
    │
    ├── hooks/
    │   └── useAuth.js            ← Custom hook to access AuthContext
    │
    ├── router/
    │   ├── index.jsx             ← All route definitions (React Router)
    │   └── PrivateRoute.jsx      ← Route guard (redirects if not logged in)
    │
    ├── layouts/                  ← Page shells with Sidebar + Header
    │   ├── AdminLayout.jsx       ← Layout for admin pages
    │   ├── StudentLayout.jsx     ← Layout for student pages
    │   ├── TeacherLayout.jsx     ← Layout for teacher pages
    │   └── Layout.module.css     ← Shared layout styles
    │
    ├── components/               ← Shared/reusable UI components
    │   ├── Sidebar.jsx           ← Navigation sidebar (role-based links)
    │   ├── Sidebar.module.css
    │   ├── Header.jsx            ← Top header bar
    │   └── Header.module.css
    │
    └── pages/
        ├── LandingPage.jsx           ← Public home/landing page
        ├── LandingPage.module.css
        ├── LoginPage.jsx             ← Login form (all roles)
        ├── LoginPage.module.css
        ├── NotFound.jsx              ← 404 page
        │
        ├── admin/                    ← Admin portal pages
        │   ├── Dashboard.jsx             ← Admin dashboard (stats overview)
        │   ├── Dashboard.module.css
        │   ├── UserManagement.jsx        ← Manage all users
        │   ├── UserManagement.module.css
        │   ├── DepartmentManagement.jsx  ← Add/edit/delete departments
        │   ├── DepartmentManagement.module.css
        │   ├── CourseManagement.jsx      ← Add/edit/delete courses
        │   ├── CourseManagement.module.css
        │   ├── AdminNotices.jsx          ← Post/manage notices
        │   ├── AdminNotices.module.css
        │   ├── Settings.jsx              ← Admin settings
        │   └── Settings.module.css
        │
        ├── teacher/                  ← Teacher portal pages
        │   ├── Dashboard.jsx             ← Teacher dashboard
        │   ├── Dashboard.module.css
        │   ├── MyCourses.jsx             ← Courses assigned to teacher
        │   ├── MyCourses.module.css
        │   ├── Attendance.jsx            ← Mark attendance
        │   ├── Attendance.module.css
        │   ├── MarksEntry.jsx            ← Enter student marks
        │   ├── MarksEntry.module.css
        │   ├── Schedule.jsx              ← Teacher class schedule
        │   ├── Schedule.module.css
        │   ├── Notices.jsx               ← View notices
        │   └── Notices.module.css
        │
        └── student/                  ← Student portal pages
            ├── Dashboard.jsx             ← Student dashboard
            ├── Dashboard.module.css
            ├── ClassRoutine.jsx          ← Class schedule/routine
            ├── ClassRoutine.module.css
            ├── Results.jsx               ← View grades/results
            ├── Results.module.css
            ├── PaymentHistory.jsx        ← Payment records
            ├── PaymentHistory.module.css
            ├── Profile.jsx               ← Student profile
            ├── Profile.module.css
            ├── NameCorrection.jsx        ← Name correction request
            └── NameCorrection.module.css
```

---

## 🗄️ Database Schema (from migrations)

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `users` | All users — admins, teachers, students (role field differentiates) |
| `students` | Student-specific profile data (linked to users) |
| `teachers` | Teacher-specific profile data (linked to users) |
| `departments` | Academic departments (CSE, EEE, BBA, etc.) |
| `semesters` | Semester records (Spring 2026, Fall 2025, etc.) |
| `courses` | Course catalog |
| `course_offerings` | Course offered in a semester by a teacher |
| `enrollments` | Which students are enrolled in which course offering |
| `results` | Student grades per course |
| `cache` | Laravel cache table |
| `jobs` | Laravel queue jobs table |

---

## 🔄 How It All Connects

```
Browser
  └── React App (client/ → localhost:5173)
        ├── AuthContext  ← stores JWT token + user info
        ├── Router       ← role-based routing (admin/teacher/student)
        ├── Layouts      ← Sidebar + Header shell
        ├── Pages        ← actual page content
        └── apiService   ← makes HTTP requests to →
              Laravel API (server/ → localhost:8000)
                ├── routes/api.php      ← route definitions
                ├── Controllers/        ← handle requests
                ├── Models/             ← query the database
                └── MySQL (XAMPP)       ← data storage
```

---

## 📌 Key Files to Know

| File | Why it matters |
|---|---|
| `server/.env` | DB connection, app key, CORS origin |
| `server/routes/api.php` | All backend API endpoints |
| `server/app/Http/Controllers/AuthController.php` | Login logic |
| `server/database/seeders/UserSeeder.php` | Where test credentials come from |
| `client/src/api/apiService.js` | Base URL & all API calls |
| `client/src/context/AuthContext.jsx` | Auth state management |
| `client/src/router/index.jsx` | All frontend routes |
| `client/src/router/PrivateRoute.jsx` | Route protection logic |
